Senior Corporate Structuring Associate, Dubai, 7+ PQE
Senior Corporate Structuring Associate, Dubai, 7+ PQE
Location:  --Dubai
This leading regional law firm is looking for a bilingual (Arabic / English) Senior Associate for their Corporate Structuring Practice in Dubai. This is a senior position and you will be working directly with the head of department.
The practice advises clients on the optimal corporate structures to achieve their business and commercial objectives. The teams experience also includes structuring, restructuring and reorganising onshore and free zone corporate entities and clients include major blue chip organisations, financial institutions, government bodies and FMCG’s throughout the Gulf and wider MENA region. Advice is given on a range of issues, including M&A transactions, legal due diligence, joint ventures and drafting and negotiating commercial agreements.
If you have the necessary skills and experience, please contact Hannah in our Dubai Office on +971 4455 8419 or send your CV and covering email to hannah@jlegal.com
